SCHEMA: universe/tier_taxonomy.schema
schema_id: dominium.schema.universe.tier_taxonomy
schema_version: 1.0.0
stability: core

PURPOSE:
- Define ordered fidelity tiers and required invariants on collapse/expand transitions.

REQUIRED SHAPE:
record tier_taxonomy
  required:
    - taxonomy_id: id
    - tiers: [id]
    - collapse_required_invariants: [id]
    - expand_redaction_rules: [id]
    - extensions: map
